text: The Haitian Creole Wikipedia is the Haitian Creole-language edition of Wikipedia. It was started in August 2004. In October 2020, it had over 60,000 articles.List of Wikipedias on Meta-Wiki. ==References== ==Other websites== *Haitian Creole Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2004
